{"tid":2254164,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"我屌你咩「為食小樂」，正仆街黎","createTime":"2020-10-22T15:28:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T16:20:30.000Z","uid":196227,"like":5,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"609510ecad044cfb5118cef51549087fe436e6a7","tid":2254164,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T15:28:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xOaQtTVlBU0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FxOaQtTVlBU0&d=LL0CSI02xgrrxVkOh%2Fu%2FREBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=13a560cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xOaQtTVlBU0</a><br />\n<br />\n啱啱食完飯出條宵夜片出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到我又想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我減緊肥呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n燒茄子好似好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，加個車仔麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n飲食界youtuber<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 為食小樂(睇野食）<br />\n- Yellowland（睇訪問）<br />\n- Jer仔（睇佢鳩）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你班仆街出多啲片呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"152b6e6ebb99a935826d8a51916e9b0b686fb015","tid":2254164,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T15:29:34.000Z","msg":"希望聽日早小小打風<br />\n我返早呀<br />\n好想放假<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"befea45432a5fb5c89a1af9fb27645f5bd525968","tid":2254164,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T15:34:47.000Z","msg":"佢好似好冇精神咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪有咩唔開心<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n話說佢塊面圓咗好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ca7858c80b5a67b831712623c046074db43b2e5","tid":2254164,"uid":168389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1